Pen test basic commands - Kali Linux
üîê Important Legal Note
Network sniffing without permission is illegal under IT Act (India) and cyber laws globally.
Use only for:
Cybersecurity labs
Ethical hacking practice
Your own network audits
sudo tcpdump -i eth0 - capture all traffic on an interface
sudo tcpdump -i wlan0 -w capture.pcap - capture and save to a file
sudo tcpdump -i eth0 tcp port 80 - capture only http traffic
sudo tcpdump -i eth0 host 192.168.1.10 - capture traffic from specific IP
sudo tcpdump -i eth0 tcp - capture only tcp packets

